It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes an efficient inference algorithm for conditional random fields. Additionally, it could be classified under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves developing algorithms for intelligent systems. The paper also deals with natural language processing (cs.CL) as it mentions labeling, which is a common task in NLP. Finally, it could be classified under multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with image processing.
